text: Kabongo Mulumba is a Democratic Republic of the Congo karateka. He won a bronze medal at the 2019 African Karate Championships in the men's –84 kg category.KABONGO MULUMBA.Kabongo Mulumba ==References== Category:Democratic Republic of the Congo male karateka Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
